## WooCommerce data-safety (HARD GATE)
- HPOS enabled; access orders via CRUD API only — never raw SQL on order tables.
- Orders, customers and payment data are NEVER deployed and NEVER committed.
- CI runs on MySQL/MariaDB ONLY (no SQLite) — order/HPOS behavior is engine-specific.
- Any change to checkout, cart totals or payment gateways requires an explicit HUMAN GATE
  before merge; wp-security-reviewer must sign off. guard-woo-data.sh enforces this.
